Dialogue: 3,0:01:48.75,0:01:49.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:53.59,Signage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(275,679)\fs39\fscy90\pos(1218,961.5)}Anti-anjelska operačná centrála
Dialogue: 3,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tiež by sme sa mali vydať?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, hej, počkaj minútku.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:52.55,0:01:54.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kedy si sa vôbec stal naším spojencom?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:54.84,0:01:56.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph.  To sa pýtaš tak neskoro?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:56.66,0:01:58.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Očividne opravujem vašu neschopnosť.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:58.23,0:01:59.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už si zabudol, ty odpad?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zúfalo zmizni ako toaletný papier!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo si to povedal?!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počúvajte, vy dvaja...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade je tam vonku a robí pre nás, čo môže.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pri tejto príležitosti...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Budeme musieť zohnať každého člena Bojiska, akého len môžeme.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:18.95,0:02:19.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:19.94,0:02:21.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa tu deje?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:22.28,0:02:25.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myslíme, že sme pripravené to skončiť.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:25.16,0:02:28.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pochopili sme to potom, čo sme počuli tvoj prejav.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozhodli sme sa.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:31.06,0:02:32.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taká sme skupina.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:32.67,0:02:35.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj bez toho, aby sme to počuli, sme to už akosi pochopili.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naša vokalistka už zmizla.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:38.38,0:02:41.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Za Iwasawu-san a Yui už žiadna náhrada nie je.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:42.68,0:02:45.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj keď jej spev bol dosť zlý.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Každý deň bol vzrušujúci, akoby bol Kultúrny festival.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:48.38,0:02:49.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bola to kopa zábavy.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:50.62,0:02:53.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No tých mimo našej skupiny bude asi ťažké presvedčiť.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asi hej, hm?
Dialogue: 3,0:02:55.73,0:02:58.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak to urobíš, tak to aj dokonči.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:58.19,0:02:59.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak nie...
Dialogue: 3,0:02:59.67,0:03:02.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bude to vyzerať, že si nás presviedčal zbytočne.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:03.16,0:03:07.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak toto Bojisko, ktoré vydržalo tak dlho, ide zmiznúť...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:07.33,0:03:12.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chcem si myslieť, že tento svet a aj ty ste si splnili svoj účel.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A budeme mať pocit, že sa z toho stáva lepšie miesto.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pre nás, aj keď len na krátky čas...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mladosť, ktorú sme predtým nemohli zažiť...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:21.51,0:03:25.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cítiť, že sme mali aspoň niečo dobré...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:25.26,0:03:28.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že je to viac, než dosť.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O čom to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Určite nemám ani tušenia.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jasné, že nie.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nuž, nevieme, čo sa stane teraz.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už pomaly pôjdeme.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je k tomu všetko.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak ahoj,
Dialogue: 3,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nováčik.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vytvoríme kapelu aj nabudúce.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:46.62,0:03:47.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Určite ju budem znova milovať.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahoj.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže si odrezal prostých občanov.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobrá práca.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:57.47,0:04:00.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tvoja povaha je vážne hrozná!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moja povaha nie je hrozná!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:01.98,0:04:04.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo si myslíš, že vravíš Bohovi?!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prestaňte sa tu hrať, poďme.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koľko ich to je?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa to deje?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kde sú NPC?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz to vyzerá tak, že títo sú jediní, čo tu zostali!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To, čo plánujeme urobiť...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to, že si to uvedomili.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph.  Blbci.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:38.75,0:04:39.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noda!?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na teba sa môžeme vždy spoľahnúť, Noda!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Budeš bojovať s nami?!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:46.59,0:04:47.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nebuď debil!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:47.80,0:04:51.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja sa hýbem, len keď tým môžem byť užitočný Yurippe!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haha. Mám ťa.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozhodne si oddaný.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ooyama?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Viem, že nemám žiadne kladné predpoklady,
Dialogue: 3,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no ak sa mi bude dobre dariť tu,
Dialogue: 3,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,tak bude snáď aj Boh prekvapený!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ukáž mu, čo si zač!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nenechám vás zabudnúť na mňa.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:18.74,0:05:22.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že by si nikto ani nevšimol, keby som teraz zmizol!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.67,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,WOOHOOOOO!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.13,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,COME ON, COME ON, COME ON, COME ON, COME OOOON!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.43,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,Knocking on Heaven's door.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je Bob Dylan...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, na túto situáciu sa to hodí.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to znamená?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:38.75,0:05:39.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto vie?!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to, že sa všetci začínajú zbierať.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je s týmto svetom?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa to tu deje?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Skôr čo sa deje s tebou.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto sakra si?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chvíľu som trénoval v horách, ale...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:58.93,0:06:00.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nebolo tam skoro nič na jedenie.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty si... Matsushita piaty?!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.17,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,Tastyyyyyy CANDY!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:05.17,0:06:07.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dosť si schudol.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je tvoje telo v poriadku?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.  Vlastne sa má lepšie ako inokedy.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:11.39,0:06:15.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz sa cítim, že by som zvládol aj stonásobné Kumite!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je karate, nie?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je jedno, pomáha to.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V každom prípade, teraz nemáme žiadne vojsko.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roztrhajme ich a poďme odtiaľto.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:25.56,0:06:27.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My všetci.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.03,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Wild Heaven.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:30.78,0:06:31.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fajn!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poďme ich preraziť!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.75,Signage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(237,479)\fs42\fscy90\pos(1213.5,961.5)}Priechod do Guildy - B2
Dialogue: 3,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bolo to perfektné miesto na schovanie...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No teraz je to nepriateľské teritórium.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto by mala byť naša základňa.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asi by som ich tu mala očakávať.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V húfoch.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra. Nemajú konca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:07:00.02,Signage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,563)\fs37.5\fscy90\pos(1357.5,961.5)}Kontaktný most 1
Dialogue: 3,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi-san. Pozri dole!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delia sa rýchlejšie než predtým.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Za tebou!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,100 ľudí.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:16.20,0:07:16.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,100 ľudí.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vaša sila sa zvýšila o 100 ľudí.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechápeš?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už to nechaj na mne.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:25.00,0:07:25.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Choď!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiina...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zbytok nechám na tebe!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nasleduj ma, Hinata!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:31.33,0:07:32.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fajn!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kam ideme?  Otonashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:41.35,Signage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(231,600)\fs42\fscy90\pos(1213.5,961.5)}Priechod do Guildy - B7
Dialogue: 3,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ich zvyšujúci sa počet musí znamenať...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Že idem správnou cestou...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Už toho moc nemám.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S týmto počtom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikdy to nezvládnem len s pištoľou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čo urobím?{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yurippe.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:55.83,0:07:56.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chaa?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guilda bola informovaná o situácii.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz všetci členovia idú na povrch.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vezmi si toto.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boj sa blíži ku koncu?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno. Končí.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:21.77,0:08:23.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V tom prípade sa rozpustíme tiež.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:24.52,0:08:28.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Podarilo sa nám zájsť až sem, lebo vy všetci ste za nás bojovali.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem vám za všetko.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:31.21,0:08:32.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keby nebolo teba...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nikdy by sme nemohli ani začať.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nikdy som nebol nič iné, než osamelý blázon.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:39.98,0:08:40.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zbohom.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:46.32,0:08:47.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je čas ísť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.67,Signage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(234,559)\fs39\fscy90\pos(1221,961.5)}Jedáleň akadémie, interiér
Dialogue: 3,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zašla som príliš ďaleko?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.94,Signage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(235,595)\fs45\fscy90\pos(1309.5,967.5)}Stará Guilda
Dialogue: 3,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čas na krátku prestávku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anjel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nie... Kanade-chan. Rozmýšľam, či tiež bojuje.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A rozmýšľam, čo by sa stalo, ak by som ju pochopila skôr.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:25.62,0:09:29.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je možné, že by sme spolu dobre vychádzali.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Predsa len sme obe dievčatá.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aj v tomto svete...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Možno by sme sa spolu mohli popozerať po oblečení alebo tak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nakoniec sa to nemohlo stať.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nemôžem mu odpustiť.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Preto...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:54.48,0:09:55.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zmiznite.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zmiznite.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zmiznite.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zmiznite!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zmiznite!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zmiznite!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zmiznite!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:15.59,0:10:21.70,Dialogue-Top,,0,0,0,,Takže... je veľmi dôležité, aby ste si zapamätali tento vzorec...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:10:18.80,0:10:21.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mám pocit, akoby som nad niečím rozmýšľala...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čo to bolo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:10:22.89,0:10:23.68,Dialogue-Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Teraz to zmažem.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.35,Dialogue-Top,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dobre?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He?{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je, Nakamura?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžem to zmazať?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:31.11,0:10:33.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, áno, len do toho.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Awww sakra!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aké ponižujúce.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:44.49,0:10:45.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, Yuri.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo si robila uprostred hodiny?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vlastne nič.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Len som nad niečím rozmýšľala.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Premýšľala o čom?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zdalo sa mi, že si bola skôr duchom neprítomná...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Žeby láska?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Premýšľala si o láske, však?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:59.09,0:10:59.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hlupaňa.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keby som mala o kom takom premýšľať...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:01.72,0:11:06.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Myslím, že by si sa hodila k Fujiwarovi-kun, Yuri.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počúvaš ma, Yuri?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:10.54,0:11:11.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, pozri.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fujiwara-kun je teraz úplne sám.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fujiwara-kuuu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 3,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, nerob to...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:16.94,0:11:20.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkať... kto vlastne si?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som Hitomi.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... áh.  Hitomi.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správne.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.95,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deje sa niečo?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presne ako som si myslela...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zase povieš, že je to láska, však?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:34.71,0:11:35.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správne!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Choď späť na miesto.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.13,0:11:37.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fajn.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tak...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uistite sa, že si túto časť dobre zapamätáte.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamura.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kam sa pozeráš?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, Yuri.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:49.06,0:11:49.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre, Nakamura.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečítaj od vrchu ďalšiu stranu.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?  Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máme strašné šťastie, nemyslíte?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:04.41,0:12:06.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... o čom to hovoríš?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:07.41,0:12:10.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vidím strašne šťastný pohľad.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to na mňa príliš.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci žijete v prítomnosti.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Musí to byť skvelé.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vážne vám závidím.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak odtiaľto zmiznem...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Premýšľam, či to môžem skúsiť celé odznova.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:23.30,0:12:26.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto šťastie, ktoré sa zdá tak prirodzené...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naozaj ho dokážem prijať?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamura...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So stratenými spomienkami...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So zmenenou osobnosťou...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V tom prípade by som to zvládla.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale potom...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dá sa to nazvať novým začiatkom?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už to viac nie je môj život.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je niekoho iného.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:50.24,0:12:53.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Verím, že máme len jeden život.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je práve tu...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Len jeden.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto je môj život.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nikomu ho nedám.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.26,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ani mi ho nikto nezoberie.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem ho vnútiť niekomu inému.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem ho zabudnúť.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem ho vymazať.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem ho pošliapať nohami.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem ho odsmiať.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:11.18,0:13:12.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem predstierať, že bol dobrý.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem s tým nič robiť!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetko je to, čím je...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kruté, no nenahraditeľné.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetko, čo môžeme urobiť, je prijať náš jeden jediný život.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pán učiteľ... chápete ma?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Preto bojujem.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Preto budem aj naďalej bojovať.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lebo...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taký život...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By som nikdy nemoha prijať!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daj mi ruku!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to, že sme to zvládli.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi-kun a... Hinata-kun?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja som tu tiež...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zvládla som to...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som späť...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tvoj hlas... nie...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tvoje spomienky explodovali a...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade sa bála a priniesla nás sem.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:08.78,0:14:09.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade-chan?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To vďaka vám.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zachránili ste ma.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:18.67,0:14:21.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale prečo ste tu dole?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechali sme to na nich.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:23.50,0:14:27.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ostatní to zobrali za nás.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A preto ste ma prišli zachrániť?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:29.89,0:14:32.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci sme bojovali spoločne.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie je to to isté, ako vždy?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asi je.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeme si pomôcť, ale bojíme sa o teba, Yurippe.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chceš si zatiaľ opraviť oblečenie?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre, hýbme sa!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hej...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Človeče.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je rovnaká ako vždy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:01.33,Signage,,0,0,0,,{\fad(236,516)\fs42\fscy90\pos(1213.5,961.5)}Priechod do Guildy - B20
Dialogue: 3,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:03.63,0:15:04.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tam dole...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevyzerá to, ako keby niečo ochraňovali?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aká náhoda.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:07.67,0:15:08.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tiež som o tom premýšľala.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:09.30,0:15:13.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale... potrebovali by sme bomby, aby sme to s nimi vybavili...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak teda idem na to.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:14.55,0:15:15.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade-chan!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je cvok.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je ako samovražda.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:23.52,0:15:24.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie, počkať...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:31.49,0:15:32.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jo!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bojová sila toho dievčaťa je väčšia, než bombardérov?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poďme.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:43.96,0:15:44.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je ich ešte viac!
Dialogue: 3,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuri, ty choď napred.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sa postaráme o týchto.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre, spolieham sa na vás.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, nechaj to na nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.27,Sign-Room,,0,0,0,,{\shad3\4a&HA0&\fs90\c&H4B452A&\frz355\pos(1303.333,346.667)\frx4\fry32\org(1014,419.333)}Počí{\c&H292C18&}tačová miestnosť 2
Dialogue: 3,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zosmiešňujú ma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale... tentokrát určite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koľko ich sakra zobral?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Niet o tom pochýb.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobrá práca, že ste to zvládli až sem.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snažíš sa ma zosmiešniť?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spraviť ten okázalý štítok...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, predsa len, toto je škola.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zdá sa, že máš zaujímavé hodnoty.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:44.69,0:16:48.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie, nie, to je proste pravidlo.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tohoto sveta...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:50.90,0:16:51.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boh?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boh.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Existuje, alebo nie?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:54.98,0:16:57.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Skutočne hlboká otázka.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Veľmi zaujímavé.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nie som v pozícii, aby som určil odpoveď.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Len dodržiavam stanovené pravidlá.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tvoje akcie boli naprogramované, že?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presne podľa tvojich predpokladov.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto ťa naprogramoval?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj keby som ti dal meno, nebol by v tom žiadny rozdiel.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to človek, ktorý tu bol dávno pradávno.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Angel Player...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je to za softvér?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako už vieš...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:24.02,0:17:28.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to softvér, ktorý dokáže vytvárať a meniť materiály tohoto sveta.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako to dokáže robiť?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:30.36,0:17:33.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto vie?  Predsa len nie som vývojár.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:33.99,0:17:37.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No vy ľudia ste vytvorili zbrane zo zeme.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to asi ten istý nápad.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nakoniec sme obaja využívali rovnaké pravidlá.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:17:46.83,0:17:50.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snažil sa vývojár tohoto softvéru stať Bohom?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto vie? Nemám tušenia.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fajn. Nemám moc času, takže sa presuňme k hlavnej otázke.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:57.18,0:18:01.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pod akými okolnosťami bolo tvoje programovanie aktivované?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neviem obsah programu.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak mi dovoľ preformulovať moju otázku.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:06.69,0:18:09.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa stalo v tomto svete, že ťa to prebudilo?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V tomto svete...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Začala rozkvitať láska.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:15.24,0:18:15.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Láska?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno, láska.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tá v tomto svete nemá existovať.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chápem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je to pravda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:18:26.16,0:18:30.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ak by sa naučili milovať, hneď by sme všetci zmizli.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No ak by začala rozkvitať, čo by sa stalo tomuto svetu?{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak by tu rozkvitla láska...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Z tohoto miesta by sa stal večný raj.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No tento svet sa takýmto miestom nesmie stať.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lebo toto je miesto, kde...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kde vlastne musíme odmaturovať.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bol tu niekto, kto tomu veril, čo?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:49.14,0:18:50.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tak...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak bol niekto, kto žil svoj život pre dobro ostatných...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bola mu poslaná jeho posledná odmena...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:54.36,0:18:58.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No stratil by spomienky a prišiel by sem...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vtedy by sa mohli začať objavovať chyby.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:01.07,0:19:05.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A to je programátor Angel Player?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som užasnutý.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máš dobrý nadhľad.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:08.37,0:19:12.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tá osoba sa dozvedela o chybách v tomto svete a začala ich meniť.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:12.63,0:19:15.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak by niekto zažil chybu, Kage by ich premenili na NPC.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:15.59,0:19:16.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inými slovami, reštart.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:17.38,0:19:17.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak čo to teda je?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:19.30,0:19:23.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Medzi NPC sú aj iní, ktorí sú ako my?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sú.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Len jeden.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Úbohá duša.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to programátor.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čakal celý ten čas.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.02,0:19:38.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na dievča, ktoré miloval, ktoré opustilo tento svet.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie je možné stretnúť sa znova.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to astronomické číslo,
Dialogue: 3,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no pravdepodobnosť nie je nulová.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:46.28,0:19:50.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No čas, ktorý strávil čakaním na ňu, bol príliš dlhý,
Dialogue: 3,0:19:50.37,0:19:53.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a nebol schopný ponechať si zdravý rozum.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:53.00,0:19:57.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Preto vytvoril program, ktorý by ho premenil na NPC.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:57.63,0:20:00.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alebo to spravil ako prvé...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:00.67,0:20:04.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A potom aplikoval opatrenia, aby zabezpečil, že sa taká vec už nikdy nebude opakovať?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to možnosť.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:06.81,0:20:10.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nastane aspoň deň, kedy tá osoba bude spokojná?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto vie?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je ťažké vedieť, čo je presne správne.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ani ja neviem, čo je správne alebo zlé.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:18.23,0:20:21.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No ty, ktorá si to zvládla až sem...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:21.49,0:20:24.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno budeš schopná objaviť odpoveď.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo tým myslíš?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:26.74,0:20:30.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Podľa tvojej vôle, mohla by si zmeniť tento svet.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tým myslím.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zmeniť? Ako?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžeš sa vydať na cestu, ktorou sa on nemohol.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:37.46,0:20:41.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Myslíš... mohla by som sa stať Bohom?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inými slovami...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mohla by som premeniť tento svet na večný raj?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:47.18,0:20:49.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On tú možnosť odmietol, no...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja nie.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno by som mal povedať, že nechcem mať emócie, aby som ju odmietol.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boh?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:57.56,0:20:59.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja, Boh tohoto sveta?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deje sa niečo?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je konečne v mojich rukách.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tento svet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Konečne som...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dôvod, pre ktorý som celý ten čas bojovala, bol tento moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mohla by som poraziť aj Anjela.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So silou tohoto systému...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:21:23.72,0:21:25.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By som bola najsilnejšia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nikdy by som neurobila takú vec.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ani Kanade-chan,
Dialogue: 3,0:21:36.19,0:21:37.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nemôžem jej to urobiť.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lebo ja...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:40.40,0:21:42.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dôvod, pre ktorý som prišla až sem...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:44.86,0:21:45.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Práve som cítil lásku.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Najsilnejšiu, akú som kedy cítil.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:52.79,0:21:54.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zväčšuje sa desivou rýchlosťou.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:57.37,0:21:58.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je to?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:59.21,0:22:00.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretože...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:00.21,0:22:02.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dôvod, pre ktorý som prišla až sem, je...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aby som každého ochránila!
Dialogue: 3,0:22:04.80,0:22:07.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áh, takže ty si zdroj.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:08.51,0:22:11.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže, čo plánuješ robiť?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:11.60,0:22:14.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vypni všetky stroje.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:14.22,0:22:15.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okamžite.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:15.56,0:22:16.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si si istá?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.98,0:22:19.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Premyslela si si to?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:19.17,0:22:21.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stále máš kopu času.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:21.31,0:22:23.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vlastne večnosť.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:24.07,0:22:26.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Niečo ťa naučím.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:26.65,0:22:27.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My ľudia...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:28.78,0:22:30.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ani desať minút...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:30.72,0:22:33.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeme počkať ani tak dlho!
Dialogue: 3,0:23:11.11,0:23:12.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Teraz už...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:23:12.66,0:23:13.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je koniec?{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:23:14.83,0:23:16.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Určite...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:23:16.29,0:23:18.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Všetci sú teraz v bezpečí...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:23:18.79,0:23:20.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Teraz musia bezpečne...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Odísť z tohoto sveta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aj keď...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aká chyba.{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.55,0:23:29.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sestra...{\i0}
Dialogue: 3,0:23:29.76,0:23:31.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Presne tak, ako vy traja.{\i0}
